'''Boorama''' ama''' Boorame''' waa magaalo madaxda gobolka [[Awdal]], sidoo kalana waa dagmo ka mid ah dagmaamadiisa. Magaalada Boorama waxa ay ku taala dhinaca galbeed ee dalka [[Soomaliland]] / [[Soomaliya]]. Magaalada Boorama waxa ay ahayd halkii lagu sameeyay wasaaradahii u horeeyey ee dalka [[Soomaliland]], sidoo kale waxa ay ahayd halkii lagu asaasay ciidamada qaranka [[Somliland]] laguna soo doortay madaxwaynahii hore Allaha u naxaristee [[Maxamed Xaaji Ibraahim Cigaal]], kana soo jeedo madaxwaynaha hadda xilka haya ee [[Daahir Riyaale Kaahin]].
